 <section class="about section-container"></section>
        <p class="about">We’re laying the foundation for a beauty movement that celebrates real girls, in real life.  Moisten [moi-suh n] is a new way of thinking about (and shopping for)  beauty products. Because “beauty” should be fun, easy, imperfect, and personal. Above all, we believe that you give life to products-products don’t breathe life into you.</p> 
    </section>